        <h3>Why Modding</h3>
        <p>You may be asking why do people want to modify the game. The basic reason is to make their game to be more personalized, to enhance the gameplay and immersion, these are are just a few of a dozen reasons. And modding prolongs the lifespan, the longevity of the game, it's one of the reason why Skyrim is still alive despite it being 11 years old.</p>
